{"about_the_game":"Step into the world of watch restoration, where each mechanism hides its secrets. You run your own well-equipped workshop, which contains all the necessary tools to restore these magnificent mechanisms to their former glory. Your workshop attracts clients from around the world, each potentially bringing a unique model, from antique pocket watches to modern smartwatches.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3088960/extras/1.gif?t=1725435819\" /><br><br>Your skills enable you to restore even the most neglected timepieces to their former splendor. Whether it\u2019s replacing worn parts, cleaning rusted mechanisms, or precise calibration \u2013 each order is a new challenge. You have complete freedom to decide how to restore functionality and shine to each watch.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3088960/extras/2.gif?t=1725435819\" /><br><br>However, remember that there is no room for error in this work. One careless move can result in irreversible damage to the watch, leading to loss of client trust and financial consequences for your workshop. Every detail matters, and each watch requires a different approach and the use of different tools.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3088960/extras/3.gif?t=1725435819\" /><br><br>Each client expects you to return a watch that not only works flawlessly but also impresses with its appearance. Face the diverse projects \u2013 from delicate repairs of the mechanism to full restorations of neglected antiques. Your work is not only technical skill but also an art that requires sensitivity and creativity.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3088960/extras/4.gif?t=1725435819\" />","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/